   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject Sixty-seven THE BLOOD OF THE COVENANT Scripture: Matt 26:28</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>This gospel message is suitable for the intellectual.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>The problem between man and God Due to man s sin, man is not right with God.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Man lost God because of his sin, and man also lost all the blessings given by God.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Man s sin also caused him to come under the judgment of God.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The Lord Jesus accomplished redemption for man The Lord Jesus died on the cross to accomplish man s redemption according to the requirement of the righteousness of God.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>The redeeming blood takes away man s sins before God.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>The blood of the Lord Jesus reconciles man to God.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>The blood of the Lord Jesus brought man back to God and recovered God s blessing upon man.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>The blood of the covenant The blood which the Lord Jesus shed on the cross not only paid the price of redemption, but also was the seal of the covenant.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>In the age of grace, God not only accomplished redemption for us, but also made a covenant with us.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>In this covenant, He promised to forgive our sins and restore our relationship with God, so that man might be able to receive all the blessings given by Him.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>The blood of the Lord Jesus is the price and the seal of this covenant.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>When we receive the blood of the Lord Jesus, we receive the price of the redemption of sins and receive the seal of this covenant.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>Therefore, when we receive the blood, our sins are forgiven, and we also have the seal of forgiveness.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>How to receive the blood of Christ Confess that you are sinful and that you are not right with God.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>Confess that the shedding of the blood of Christ on the cross is for your redemption.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>Receive Christ and His redemption.</S>
   </TEXT>
